    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Concept having to do with the state or condition of habitual reliance upon a narcotic, opiate, or hallucinogen for psychotropic rather than medicinal purposes. For excessive use or misuse of drugs, use "drug abuse."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000046415/Concise Medical Dictionary (1998)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Adicción a narcóticos u otras drogas. Para el uso excesivo o abuso de drogas, usar "abuso de drogas".</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
